// Log on Grail upgrade state for this tenant, derived from observed log ingest by storage
// backend over the dashboard timeframe ("Elasticsearch" = Log Classic, "Grail" = Logs app).
// The per-backend ingest metric is the source of truth — no configuration setting is read.
